{"tid":2166323,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"絕食52日 青山灣羈留者再被毆","createTime":"2020-08-20T10:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T10:57:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"093c785db8d759a5e948c585e3d1b8768af36481","tid":2166323,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:49:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/42XFC7FASJAR3LHTIYTH3IHE3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2F42XFC7FASJAR3LHTIYTH3IHE3E%2F&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5VYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=1765e54e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2F42XFC7FASJAR3LHTIYTH3IHE3E%2F&h=c26ecb25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/42XFC7FASJAR3LHTIYTH3IHE3E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n絕食52日 青山灣羈留者再被毆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/i5Fc3fuU7eXdRJBdeSaq569L4j0=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RNI4GZRPRNC7XKBF5PEYKNC2YQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fi5Fc3fuU7eXdRJBdeSaq569L4j0%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRNI4GZRPRNC7XKBF5PEYKNC2YQ.jpg&h=a293b620&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■CIC關注組昨發表調查報告，指逾四分三曾經或正被羈留受訪者認為遭受不人道對待。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】屯門青山灣入境事務中心（CIC）疑爆出人道危機，多名不滿被長期羈留人士發起絕食抗議。協助他們的CIC關注組表示，該批人士已絕食52日，過去一周已有兩人失去知覺送院，有人回到中心後更被毆打，並引述入境處相關人士承認有被羈留者遲遲未獲發藥治療癌症，亦有男醫生對穆斯林女性全裸搜身等，關注組已就事件報告聯合國。CIC關注組又發表調查指，逾四分三曾經或正被羈留人士認為遭受不人道對待。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關注組向聯合國發緊急呼籲<br />\n<br />\n屯門青山灣入境事務中心用作接收逾期居留人士，6月底起，中心有被羈留人士因為不滿被長期羈留而發起絕食，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n關注組表示，很多絕食者身上有不同痛症，但醫生並沒有理會他們，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n關注組認為，處方職員對發起絕食抗議的羈留者施以暴力及毆打，是報復行為，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n關注組早前訪問了100位曾經或現時被羈留的人士和訪客，當中35.9%人士曾經遭受入境處人員不准談話或禁止行動等不合理命令，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n「獨立媒體」本月9日報道青山灣入境事務中心絕食事件，入境處在12日發稿質疑報道失實。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n入境處回覆指中心內昨有11人絕食，並指有人聲稱入境處人員以言語及肢體暴力對待被羈留人士，均屬不實指控，處方深表遺憾。"},{"pid":"60d41c5ab8c216490cb8bd53de47fa0c264ab7da","tid":2166323,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:52:01.000Z","msg":"WE MUST FIGHT BACK IN OUR HOMELAND, WHATEVER WILL LOSE AND DIE LIKE A PIG.<br />\nREVENGE, OR DIE IN SHAME<br />\n<br />\n十月狂歡 不日上映<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fPknqS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fPknqS</a>"},{"pid":"5f8c773e7b80a8a4140a85841d0d8bf94f891d30","tid":2166323,"uid":58209,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:56:41.000Z","msg":"呢啲臭閪難民全部踢番去原居地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留係度把撚咩"},{"pid":"2514d03357ba335f4c77d311a4db3580d5709b25","tid":2166323,"uid":364770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f8c773e7b80a8a4140a85841d0d8bf94f891d30","tid":2166323,"uid":58209,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:56:41.000Z","msg":"呢啲臭閪難民全部踢番去原居地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留係度把撚咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:57:26.000Z","msg":"岩呀"}]}